===England vs Croatia===
The teams have previously met in eleven previous matches, including a [[2018 FIFA World Cup knockout stage#Croatia vs England|2–1 semi-final win]] in [[2018 FIFA World Cup|2018]] for Croatia to advance to their first final.<ref>{{cite web|title=England vs. Croatia Head-to-Head in the World Cups|url=https://www.thesoccerworldcups.com/head_to_head/england_vs_croatia.php|website=thesoccerworldcups.com|access-date=6 December 2025}}</ref> Their most recent meeting was in the [[UEFA Euro 2020]] group stage, with England winning [[UEFA Euro 2020 Group D#England vs Croatia|1–0]].<ref>{{cite web|title=England national football team: record v Croatia|url=https://www.11v11.com/teams/england/tab/opposingTeams/opposition/Croatia|website=11v11.com|access-date=December 6, 2025}}</ref>

